    <style type="text/css">
    	#examNextPrevious{
    		position: absolute;
		    bottom: 22px;
    	}
    	#examNextPrevious .previous{
		    float: left;
		    margin-left: 10px;
    	}
    	#examNextPrevious .next{
		    float: right;
		    margin-right: 10px;
    	}
    	.center, .center2{
    		display: none;
    	}
    	.center{
    		text-align: center;
    	}
    	.content {
		    margin: 20px auto 0 auto!important;
		    padding: 5px 20px 20px 40px!important;
    	}
    	.center>img{
		    max-height: 405px;
		    max-width: 90%;
    	}
    	.center>iframe{
		    height: 405px;
		    width: 90%;
    	}
    	.welcome{
    		background: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important;
    	}
    	.welcome .center,
    	.welcome .center2{
    		display: block;
    	}
    	.welcome #rightWrap,
    	.welcome .content ,
        .show-point #rightWrap,
        .show-point .content{
    		display: none;
    	}
    	.welcome #contentWrap,
        .show-point #contentWrap
        {
    		margin: 0;
    	}
        #contentWrap{
            overflow-y: auto;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .ansType .question{
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .ansType .result{
            display: none;
        }
        .ansType .result.open{
            display: block;
        }
        .answer-stt{
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .answer-stt.active::before{
            content: '';
            background: url(data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhEQAUAJEAAAAAAP///wBg/////yH5BAEAAAMALAAAAAARABQAAAIqnI+pi8Ir3GtxnljtwHLyznxZ+HmcMm4nlZVsi0FnTIrmeoO3ZqSajigAADs=);
            width: 16px;
            height: 20px;
            position: absolute;
            left: 3px;
            top: 8px;
        }
        #questionListenNext{
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 22px;
            display: none;
        }
        #point{
            display: none;
        }
        #point .center{
            display: block !important;
        }
        .show-point #point{
            display: block;
        }
        #point .value{
            position: absolute;
            top: 147px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 75px;
            color: #353535;
        }
        #point .center{
            position: relative;
        }
    </style>

    <script type="text/javascript">
    	const database = {
    		welcome: [
	    		(welcome)
    			{
    				img: "data:image/gif;base64,",
    				button: [
    					"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
    					"data:image/jpeg;base64,"
    				]
    			},
    			{
    				img: "data:image/gif;base64,",
    				button: [
    					"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
    					"data:image/jpeg;base64,"
    				]
    			},
    			{
    				img: "data:image/gif;base64,",
    				button: [
    					"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
    					"data:image/jpeg;base64,"
    				]
    			},
    			{
    				img: "data:image/gif;base64,",
    				button: ["", ""]
    			}
    		],
    		answerStt: [
    			'①', '②', '③', '④'
    		],
            config: {
                time_start: 1000,
                time_show_info_listen: 3000,
                password: "(password)"
            },
    		questions: (questions)
       	};

        // Khai báo các biến mang data tính toán
        var question_now = null;
        var list_answer = [];
        var show_info_read = false;
        var startTimerThis = null;
        var question_result = {};
        var question_point = 0;

    	function welcomeStep(step_i = null) {
    		step_i = Number(step_i);
    		// Check isset step 
    		if(step_i < database.welcome.length) {
	    		const step = database.welcome[step_i];
	    		$("#welcome-step .center>img").hide();
	    		$("#welcome-step .center>iframe").hide();
	    		if("video" in step) {
		    		$("#welcome-step .center>iframe").attr('src', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/'+ step.video);
	    			$("#welcome-step .center>iframe").show();
	    		} else {
	    			if(step_i > 0) $("#welcome-step .center>iframe").remove();
		    		$("#welcome-step .center>img").attr('src', step.img);
		    		$("#welcome-step .center>img").show();
	    		}

	    		$("#welcome-step .center2>a").attr('step', step_i+1);
	    		$("#welcome-step .center2 img").attr('src', step.button[0]).attr('data-src', step.button[0]).attr('src-hover', step.button[1]);
    			if(step.button[0] === "" && step.button[1] === ""){
	    			setTimeout(function(){
					    renderListAnswer();
                        $("#containerWrap").removeClass("welcome");
					}, database.config.time_start);
	    		}
    		} 
    	}

    	function renderListAnswer() {
    		var data = {
    			read: [],
    			listen: []
    		}

    		// Chia loại nghe với đọc
    		for(let index in database.questions) {
    			const row = database.questions[index];
    			const temp = {
					id: row._id,
					minute: row.minute,
				};
    			switch(Number(row.questions.type)) {
    				case 1:
    				case 2:
    				case 4:
    					data.read.push(temp);
    				break;
    				case 3:
    					data.listen.push(temp);
    			}
    		}
    		const max = data.read.length > data.listen.length ? data.read.length : data.listen.length;
    		var html = [];
    		for(let stt = 0; stt<max; stt++) {
    			let temp = '<tr>';
    			if(stt in data.read)
    				temp += `<td class="question" data-id="${data.read[stt].id}">${stt+1}</td><td id="${data.read[stt].id}"><b><span class="result">•</span></b></td>`;
    			else 
    				temp += '<td></td><td><b><span></span></b></td>';

    			if(stt in data.listen)
    				temp += `<td>${data.read.length+stt+1} </td><td id="${data.listen[stt].id}"><b><span class="result">•</span></b></td>`;
    			else 
    				temp += '<td></td><td><b><span></span></b></td>';
    			temp += '</tr>';
    			html.push(temp);
    		}
    		if(html.length < 30) {
    			for(let stt = 0; stt<30-html.length;stt++)
    				html.push('<tr><td></td><td><b><span></span></b></td><td></td><td><b><span></span></b></td></tr>');
    		}
    		$("#rightWrap .ansType tbody").html(html.join(''));

            // Lấy ra thứ tự câu hỏi
            for(let index in data.read) {
                list_answer.push(data.read[index].id);
            }
            for(let index in data.listen) {
                list_answer.push(data.listen[index].id);
            }

            questionStep(list_answer[0]);
    	}

    	function questionStep(id) {
            stopTimer();

            // Get question
            var row = null;
            for(let index in database.questions) {
                if(database.questions[index]._id === id) {
                    row = database.questions[index];
                    break;
                }
            }
            if(row === null) return;
			var stt = list_answer.indexOf(id);
            var html = {
				question: [],
				answer: []
			};
            if(!show_info_read) {
                // Kiểm tra nếu là câu nghe đầu tiên sẽ hiện thông báo mô tả
                if(stt === 0 && row.questions.type == 3) {
                    show_info_read = true;
                } else {
                    for(let index in database.questions) {
                        if(database.questions[index]._id === list_answer[stt-1]) {
                            if(row.questions.type == 3 && database.questions[index].questions.type != 3) {
                                show_info_read = true;
                            }
                            break;
                        }
                    }
                }
                if(show_info_read) {
                    // Ẩn button next read
                    $('#examNextPrevious').hide();
                    $('#questionListenNext').show();
                    $("#examTestView .qHead").html('<br /><br /><br />');
                    $("#examTestView .qType tbody").html(`<tr><td align="center" style="font-size:20px;"><b>듣기 (5문항)</b></td></tr><tr><td width="500"><hr></td></tr><tr><td align="right">*모든 듣기 문제는 두 번씩 들려 드립니다.</td></tr>`);
                    setTimeout(function() {
                        questionListenNext();                          
                    }, database.config.time_show_info_listen);
                    return;
                }
            } 
            switch(Number(row.questions.type)) {
    			case 2:
    				html.question.push(`<br><b>[${stt+1}] ${row.title}.</b><br><br>${stt+1}. ${row.note != null ? row.note : ''}<br><img src="${row.questions.image}" /><br /><br />`);
    			break;
                case 1:
                    html.question.push(`<br><b>[${stt+1}] ${row.title}.</b><br><br>${stt+1}. ${row.note != null ? row.note : ''}<br><div style="border:solid 1px #333;padding:9px;">${row.questions.text}</div><br /><br />`);
                break;
                case 3: 
                    html.question.push(`<br><b>[${stt+1}] ${row.title}.</b><br><br><audio style="display: none;" controls id="question-audio"><source src="${row.questions.audio}"></audio>`);
                	if('image' in row.questions && row.questions.image != null)
    					html.question.push(`${stt+1}. ${row.note != null ? row.note : ''}<br><img src="${row.questions.image}" /><br /><br />`);
                break;
    		}
    		let is_image = false;
    		for(let index in row.answer) {
    			if('content' in row.answer[index] && row.answer[index].content !== null) {
    				html.answer.push(`<tr answer-key="${row.answer[index].key}"><td><div class="answer-stt">${ index in database.answerStt ? database.answerStt[index] : 'NaN'} </div></td><td>${row.answer[index].content}</td></tr>`);
    			} else {
    				is_image = true;
    				html.answer.push(`<td answer-key="${row.answer[index].key}"><div class="answer-stt">${ index in database.answerStt ? database.answerStt[index] : 'NaN'} </div><img src="${row.answer[index].image}" /></td>`);
    			}
    		}
    		html.answer = html.answer.join('');
    		if(is_image) {
    			html.answer = '<tr><td><table><tbody>'+ html.answer +'</tbody></table></td></tr>';
    		}

    		$("#examTestView .qHead").html(html.question.join(''));
    		$("#examTestView .qType tbody").html(html.answer);

            question_now = id;
            showResult();
            hiddenPrevious();

            var fiveMinutes = 60 * Number(row.minute);
            var display = document.querySelector('#t_left_time');
            // Xử lý sau khi append data
            switch(Number(row.questions.type)) {
                case 3:
                    display = document.querySelector('#t_right_time');
                    setTimeout(function() {
                        document.getElementById('question-audio').play();                          
                    }, 100);
                break;
            }
            startTimer(fiveMinutes, display);
    	}

        // TRỞ LẠI CÂU HỎI TRƯỚC ĐÓ
        function questionPrevious() {
            questionStep(list_answer[list_answer.indexOf(question_now)-1]);
        }

        // Next câu hỏi
        function questionNext() {
            var id = question_now === null ? list_answer[0] : list_answer[list_answer.indexOf(question_now)+1];
            questionStep(id);
        }

        // Next câu hỏi read
        function questionListenNext() {
            var index = list_answer.indexOf(question_now)+1;
            var id = list_answer[index];
            questionStep(id);
            if(index+1 === list_answer.length){
                $("#questionListenNext").hide();
            }
        }

        // Ẩn thanh điều hướng
        function hiddenPrevious() {
            $("#examNextPrevious .previous").show();
            $("#examNextPrevious .next").show();
            if(list_answer.indexOf(question_now) === 0) {
                $("#examNextPrevious .previous").hide();
            } else if(list_answer.indexOf(question_now)+1 === list_answer.length) {
                $("#examNextPrevious .next").hide();
            }
        }

        // Next câu hỏi ở danh sách sidebar
        $(document).on('click', '.ansType .question', function() {
            if(show_info_read) return;
            const _id = $(this).attr('data-id');
            questionStep(_id);
        });
        // Đếm ngược thời gian làm đề
        function startTimer(duration, display) {
            var timer = duration, minutes, seconds;
            startTimerThis = setInterval(function () {
                minutes = parseInt(timer / 60, 10);
                seconds = parseInt(timer % 60, 10);

                minutes = minutes < 10 ? "0" + minutes : minutes;
                seconds = seconds < 10 ? "0" + seconds : seconds;

                display.textContent = minutes + ":" + seconds;

                if (--timer < 0) {
                    stopTimer();
                    questionNext();
                }
            }, 1000);
        }
        // Dừng bộ đếm thời gian lại
        function stopTimer() {
            if(startTimerThis !== null) {
                document.querySelector('#t_right_time').textContent = "04:00";
                document.querySelector('#t_left_time').textContent = "06:00";
                clearInterval(startTimerThis);
                startTimerThis = null;
            }
        }

        $(document).on('click', "#examTestView .answer-stt", function() {
            const id = $(this).parents('*[answer-key]').attr('answer-key');
            if(!(question_now in question_result)) {
                question_result[question_now] = [];
            }
            const index = question_result[question_now].indexOf(id);
            if(index < 0) {
                // Get question 
                var row = null;
                for(let index in database.questions) {
                    if(database.questions[index]._id === question_now) {
                        row = database.questions[index];
                        break;
                    }
                }
                // Check xem có chọn nhiều đáp án quá không
                if(question_result[question_now].length === row.answer.length-1) {
                    alert('Không được chọn tất cả đáp án!');
                    return;
                } 
                question_result[question_now].push(id); 
            } else {
                question_result[question_now].splice(index, 1);
            }
            showResult();
        });

        // Hiển thị các câu đã select result
        function showResult() {
            $(".ansType .result").removeClass('open');
            for(let index in question_result) {
                if(question_result[index].length > 0) {
                    $(`#${index} .result`).addClass('open');
                }
            }

            // Hiển thị tích chọn trong câu hỏi
            if(question_now in question_result) {
                $("#examTestView tr .answer-stt").removeClass('active');
                for(let index in question_result[question_now]) {
                    $(`#examTestView *[answer-key=${question_result[question_now][index]}] .answer-stt`).addClass('active');
                }
            }
        }

        function submitAnswer() {
            if(list_answer.indexOf(question_now)+1 !== list_answer.length) {
                alert("Solved all the problems, the answers can be submitted.");
                return;
            } else if(!confirm("Try testing has been shut down.")){
            	return;
            }
            // Tính điểm
            for(let index in database.questions) {
                const row = database.questions[index];
                if(!(row._id in question_result)) continue;
                let result_client = question_result[row._id];
                let result = [];
                for(let i in row.answer) {
                    if(row.answer[i].active === true) result.push(row.answer[i].key);
                }
                result.sort(function(a, b){return a-b});
                result_client.sort(function(a, b){return a-b});
                if(result.join('|') === result_client.join('|')) {
                    const point = Number(row.point);
                    if(isNaN(point)) continue;
                    question_point += point;
                }
            }
            $("#point .value").text(question_point);
            $("#containerWrap").addClass("show-point");
        }
       
		function verifyPass() {
			var password = prompt("Vui lòng nhập mậ khẩu đề mở đề!");
			if (CryptoJS.MD5(password) == database.config.password) {
		        welcomeStep(0);
			} else {
				if(confirm("Mật khẩu không đúng, bạn có muốn thử lại?")) {
					verifyPass();
				}
			}
		}
		if(database.config.password != '') {
			verifyPass();
		} else {
			welcomeStep(0);
		}

    </script>
</body>
</html>
